<p><img src="/images/fdaacleared.gif" class="float-left mr-3" width="71" height="45" />I use FDA-Cleared Essense epilators, designed and manufactured in the USA by Clareblend. Their digital technology provides precision and increased client comfort.<br clear="all" /></p>
